  "title": "Chef de Partie",
  "description": "<p>Chef de Partie</p><p>Pizza & Grill Station</p><p>Role Description:</p><ul><li>Italian restaurant - In charge of Pizza & Grill operation independently</li><li>Collaborate with other kitchen crews to prepare, clean, and organize ingredients for use during the service</li><li>Train and develop junior chefs</li><li>Maintain kitchen safety and hygiene</li><li>Oversees daily food preparation and ensures smooth coordination among kitchen stations.</li><li>Manages a first-in, first-out (FIFO) system to maintain freshness and proper food rotation.</li><li>Monitors storage areas to ensure all ingredients are properly labeled, stored, and meet hygiene standards.</li><li>﻿﻿Supervises station chefs to maintain consistency, timing, and presentation across all dishes.</li><li>﻿﻿Upholds strict food safety and sanitation practices Incompliance with health regulations.</li><li>Maintains high culinary standards and quality control for every menu item prepared.</li><li>﻿﻿Assists in planning and maintaining ingredient inventory, restocking, and placing supplier orders.</li><li> Specializes in preparing fresh pasta, hand-tossed pizza dough, and operating the grill station for meat and seafood dishes.</li><li>Customer oriented, calm under pressure and has good communication skills.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Full timer,  can start immediately</li><li>Solid hands-on experience in opening pizza by hands (wood-fired oven) & Charcoal Grill</li><li>Italian & Western cuisine trained, culinary school qualifications a plus</li><li>Food Hygiene Course or F&B officer certificate is a must.</li></ul><p>Location:</p><ul><li>Cugini Trattoria Pizzeria, 37 Joo Chiat Pl, Singapore 427761</li></ul><p>Working Hours: 5-day work week | 44hrs weekly (Rotating Shifts) | Able to work on weekends and public holidays<br /></p><p>We will offer competitive pay packages, friendly working environment and open communication amongst the team.</p>",
